{"tid":1206324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[CCTVB 10:27] 政府總部各入口已封閉 政府籲公務員不要前往政總","createTime":"2019-06-12T02:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T03:43:14.000Z","uid":231040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc093f3901be0847a2b592461e8924f021ea46b8","tid":1206324,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府總部各入口現已封閉，政府呼籲公務員不要前往政總，已回到政總的繼續留在辦公室內。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/instant/5d0062fee60383df0a92ec83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Finstant%2F5d0062fee60383df0a92ec83&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=c1ccc89f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/instant/5d0062fee60383df0a92ec83</a>"},{"pid":"700519030696a0cc022c37221e8aa9a0e02bed58","tid":1206324,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"政府總部各入口封閉 行政署籲政府人員勿前往政總<br />\n2019-06-12 HKT 10:20<br />\n<br />\n政府行政署表示，因應添馬政府總部附近道路嚴重阻塞及警方的安排，政府總部各入口現已封閉，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n行政署呼籲各政府人員請勿繼續前往總部，而已返回政府總部的同事，繼續留在辦公室內，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462272-20190612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462272-20190612.htm&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=afd1cb8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462272-20190612.htm&h=0e93184f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462272-20190612.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0e88c96ac4fe4d33a2589560ad6dc9cbf49e1071","tid":1206324,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>現場需要物資</ins></strong> -<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: violet;\">生理鹽水</span><br />\n2) <span style=\"color: violet;\">頭盔</span><br />\n3) <span style=\"color: violet;\">保鮮紙</span><br />\n4) <span style=\"color: violet;\">口罩</span><br />\n5) <span style=\"color: violet;\">膠布</span></span>"}]}